          "GW Undiagnosed Illness",
          "Gulf War Registry",
          "Hardship",
          "Homeless",
          "IDES Participant",
          "If orig CFile found conduct Phase II Nehmer Review",
          "In Receipt of Chapter 31",
          "Incarceration",
