          "Sensitive Level 6",
          "Seriously Injured/Very Seriously Injured",
          "Specially Adapted Housing Claimed",
          "Supervised Direct Pay",
          "TBI Equitable Relief Review",
          "Temporary Folder Exists",
          "Terminally Ill",
